    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1662477888\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/80f9d179358a7abac7863dd2ed0839b1.avif?t=1662477888\" width=600 height=188 /></span><br><br>The Alchemist Shop: An Apprentice's Life is a game that mixes <strong>Visual Novel</strong> and <strong>Solitaire</strong>. You play as Faih, a young alchemist that just managed to be hired by Arcani, the owner of the <strong>BEST Alchemist Shop</strong> of the continent. You will be in charge of the shop for 15 days and must deliver the best <strong>potions </strong>possible if you want to keep your job. Are you up to the task?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How To Play</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Listen to your master!</strong></h2><br>Arcani is here to guide you and make sure you do not get into trouble! I mean, in theory...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/ab0b447eb8f52212e7e69e55d1ca4344.poster.avif?t=1662477888\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/ab0b447eb8f52212e7e69e55d1ca4344.webm?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/ab0b447eb8f52212e7e69e55d1ca4344.mp4?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solitaire</strong></h2><br>You have to manage a board full of cards using a solitaire-like mechanic. You can only move a card on top of another with a value higher than theirs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/ac634285fa48daa63a4b8a435a7484b6.poster.avif?t=1662477888\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/ac634285fa48daa63a4b8a435a7484b6.webm?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/ac634285fa48daa63a4b8a435a7484b6.mp4?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create Potions</strong></h2><br>Find the right ingredients among the cards you have and place them on the slots at the middle of the table to create a potion!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/1ed5c2d26779af767a2d6700f1e8b1c7.poster.avif?t=1662477888\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/1ed5c2d26779af767a2d6700f1e8b1c7.webm?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/1ed5c2d26779af767a2d6700f1e8b1c7.mp4?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to know the right recipe?</strong></h2><br>Make sure to choose the right potions to the case! If you're unsure, do not worry! Faih is an organized person, he keeps journal with all of them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/1dfa6b2ab0b1e2896fb370a2f6043d97.poster.avif?t=1662477888\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/1dfa6b2ab0b1e2896fb370a2f6043d97.webm?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/1dfa6b2ab0b1e2896fb370a2f6043d97.mp4?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Time Limit</strong></h2><br>Time sure flies by when you're having a good time. Be aware of the time, you need to finish all recipes by the end of the day! Or else...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/eb6c48dcb993e46b10e6b3675f662f07.poster.avif?t=1662477888\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/eb6c48dcb993e46b10e6b3675f662f07.webm?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746700/extras/eb6c48dcb993e46b10e6b3675f662f07.mp4?t=1662477888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features </strong></h2><br>- Enjoy this different approach to a <strong>Solitaire </strong>game! Challenge yourself to find the right <strong>ingredients </strong>to complete your <strong>orders</strong>!<br><br>- <strong>Game Story</strong>: Succeed in 14 different challenges and dive into the story of the young Alchemist apprentice! Be aware, your <strong>choices </strong>will shape your destiny!<br><br>- A beautiful and <strong>original soundtrack</strong> will make you feel as you're the alchemist apprentice yourself!<br><br>- Enjoy the company of<strong> Faih and Arcani</strong>, they are excited to spend some time with you!<br><br>- Challenge yourself on an exciting <strong> Arcade mode</strong>, after you beat the main story!",
